snippet.title: Guidus Zero Dev Log #1
snippet.description:
Our new game Guidus Zero is under development! 
It's based on the Guidus system but simultaneously has many changes and improvements. We'll let everyone know step by step! 

If you guys want to play Guidus,  You can play it here on Google Play and App Store.

https://guidus.onelink.me/demM/63e4b90a
